FileSummary: This is a summary of the Oriental Institute's "Wonders of Ancient Egypt" tour, led by Emily Teeter, running from November 28 to December 13, 2022, including visits to Cairo, Saqqara, Giza, Luxor, Dendera, Abydos, Edfu, Kom Ombo, Aswan, and Abu Simbel. An optional Alexandria extension from December 13-16, 2022 is also available. The tour includes exclusive access to sites and scholars, with pricing details, inclusions, exclusions, and booking information provided.
